<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><span style="color:#970118"><strong><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/gallery-writing">画廊大赛</a>：速写大师</strong></span></span><br />
<span style="font-size:75%;"><strong>在开赛48小时内围绕一幅画廊图片创作一篇scp文档（包括001提案、J文档等变体），并在同类稿件中取得最高分。</strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:75%;"><strong><em>获奖用文档：<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-1184">SCP-CN-1184</a></em></strong></span><br />
<span style="font-size:60%;"><strong><em>感谢<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ylumwlne" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5450442); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5450442&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610174390" alt="Ylumwlne" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5450442)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ylumwlne" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5450442); return false;">Ylumwlne</a></span> 绘制的成就徽章。<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/ylumwlne-logo">点击这里查看当次竞赛所有成就徽章。</a></em></strong></span></p>
