				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-hormress" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4142571); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4142571&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248397" alt="Dr Hormress" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4142571)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-hormress" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4142571); return false;" >Dr Hormress</a></span> <span class="odate time_1610244777 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">10 Jan 2021 02:12</span>
																	<br/>
						讨论中 <a href="/forum/c-675245/">单页讨论 / 单页讨论</a> &raquo;
						<a href="/scp-cn-1674/comments/show">SCP-CN-1674</a>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4866438">
									

<p>收容等级&#8212;收容难度</p>
<p>并没有一个确切的规则说你必须要用哪个等级<br />
我感觉即使无法收容，直接没等级也是不合适的</p>
<hr />
<p>对了，这不是叙事层类项目</p>

