		<div class="post" id="post-4866435">
		<div class="long">
			<div class="head">
								<div class="title" id="post-title-4866435">
																	<a href="/scp-cn-1581/comments/show#post-4866435"></a>
									</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fwuntidy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4216903); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4216903&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248397" alt="fwUntidy" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4216903)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fwuntidy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4216903); return false;" >fwUntidy</a></span> <span class="odate time_1610244527 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">10 Jan 2021 02:08</span>
																	<br/>
						讨论中 <a href="/forum/c-675245/">单页讨论 / 单页讨论</a> &raquo;
						<a href="/scp-cn-1581/comments/show">SCP-CN-1581</a>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4866435">
									

<p>除去没有用引用方块外，觉得格式怪大概是太短了吧。短篇不胜于格式而是胜于一个令人灵光一闪的点子（优秀的短篇往往意味深长，使人产生联想），当一个点子不出众的短篇出现时就会开始关注格式自然觉得怪。以上，建议这篇的作者还是写长一些，在没有极惊艳的点子时。</p>

							</div>

								
					
						<div class="options">
				
																			</div>
									
			<div id="post-options-4866435" class="options" style="display: none">
			</div>
