			<div class="content" id="post-content-4866360">
									

<p>謝謝建議！</p>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;显示里面的东西</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;隐藏里面的东西</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p>不過我這樣寫的原因是為了表現出SCP的習性也與向日葵相關，有喜光特點，晚上會停止活動。這一點在後文中也稍稍照應到了一點：</p>
<blockquote>
<p>我们每天很早就睡觉，他们有时候还会说我睡得太熟了，而且我每次都是第一个起床的。</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
</div>
</div>

							</div>

								
					
						<div class="options">
				
																			</div>
									
			<div id="post-options-4866360" class="options" style="display: none">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="short">
						<a class="title" href="javascript:;" ></a> 由 <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twilit" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6592438); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6592438&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610248398" alt="Twilit" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6592438)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twilit" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6592438); return false;" >Twilit</a></span>, <span class="odate time_1610236011 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">09 Jan 2021 23:46</span>
		</div>
