<p>1. <strong>图书馆</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/wanderers:little-red-riding-hood">小红帽</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhi-zi-jiu-jun" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4326424); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4326424&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610174390" alt="zhi_zi-jiu_jun" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4326424)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhi-zi-jiu-jun" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4326424); return false;">zhi_zi-jiu_jun</a></span></li>
<li><em>小红帽常常会忘记自己是一只狼。</em></li>
</ul>
<p>2. <strong>农历新年</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/happy-new-year-my-love">新年快乐！</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/austinyzhao" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3968381); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3968381&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610174390" alt="AustinYZhao" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3968381)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/austinyzhao" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3968381); return false;">AustinYZhao</a></span></li>
<li><em>不论发生何事，过新年一事总不会落下。</em></li>
</ul>
